    <item>
      <title>尼基·哈利的支持者认为她没有机会获得共和党提名。他们不在乎</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/nikki-haley-supporters-dont-think-she-has-shot-gop-nomination-they-dont-care-2024-03-04/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[妮基·哈利 (Nikki Haley) 在她的总统竞选活动中吸引了最多的人群。她刚刚获得了两位美国参议员的支持。她正在向比以往更加喧闹的人群展示自信的表演——尽管几乎没有人认为她会获胜。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/nikki-haley-supporters-dont-think-she-has-shot-gop-nomination-they-dont-care-2024-03-04/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 11:02:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国立法者投票将堕胎列为宪法权利</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/french-lawmakers-hold-vote-make-abortion-constitutional-right-2024-03-04/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国立法者周一开会进行最终投票，将堕胎权纳入宪法，这是世界上首次受到女权组织欢迎，但遭到反堕胎组织批评的法案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/french-lawmakers-hold-vote-make-abortion-constitutional-right-2024-03-04/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 10:52:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦谢巴兹·谢里夫宣誓就任总理</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistans-shehbaz-sharif-takes-oath-prime-minister-2024-03-04/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦谢赫巴兹·谢里夫周一宣誓，第二次正式就任总理，此前近四个星期，全国选举的不确定性导致联合政府的组建被推迟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistans-shehbaz-sharif-takes-oath-prime-minister-2024-03-04/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 10:33:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南首都河内名列污染最严重城市榜首</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/vietnamese-capital-hanoi-tops-list-most-polluted-cities-2024-03-04/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，越南首都河内的街道笼罩在浓浓的烟雾中，由于车辆排放的高浓度颗粒物和建筑相关的细尘造成空气污染，能见度大大降低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/vietnamese-capital-hanoi-tops-list-most-polluted-cities-2024-03-04/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 10:20:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>格陵兰妇女因历史上的非自愿节育将丹麦告上法庭</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/greenland-women-take-denmark-court-over-historical-involuntary-birth-control-2024-03-04/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一群格陵兰岛妇女的律师周一表示，他们正在法庭上向格陵兰前殖民统治者丹麦寻求赔偿，原因是 20 世纪 60 年代发起的非自愿节育运动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/greenland-women-take-denmark-court-over-historical-involuntary-birth-control-2024-03-04/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 10:16:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华友钴业董事长提出电池材料政策化解产能过剩</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-huayou-cobalt-chief-proposes-battery-material-policy-tackle-overcapacity-2024-03-04/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据官方媒体周一报道，浙江华友钴业董事长在中国年度人大会议之前提出，中国应采取措施解决锂电池材料行业产能过剩问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-huayou-cobalt-chief-proposes-battery-material-policy-tackle-overcapacity-2024-03-04/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 10:14:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国圣公会将解决奴隶制问题的目标扩大到 10 亿英镑</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/church-england-expand-target-address-slavery-links-1-bln-pounds-2024-03-04/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国国教已接受一个由被奴役非洲人后裔领导的监督小组建议的 10 亿英镑目标，以解决历史上与奴隶贸易的金融联系，该小组表示最初的 1 亿英镑太低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/church-england-expand-target-address-slavery-links-1-bln-pounds-2024-03-04/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 10:06:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度农民计划进入新德里加剧抗议</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indian-farmers-plan-enter-new-delhi-intensify-protests-2024-03-04/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度农民计划从周三开始升级抗议活动，乘坐公共汽车和火车进入首都新德里，并在目前被拖拉机封锁的边境口岸增加抗议人数。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indian-farmers-plan-enter-new-delhi-intensify-protests-2024-03-04/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 10:00:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合国人权事务高级专员表示避免加沙战争爆发至关重要</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/un-rights-chief-says-essential-avoid-conflagration-gaza-war-2024-03-04/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国人权事务高级专员周一表示，必须避免加沙战争进一步恶化，并警告称，任何战火都可能对整个中东及该地区以外地区产生广泛影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/un-rights-chief-says-essential-avoid-conflagration-gaza-war-2024-03-04/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 09:50:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
